<br>
The  idea was mine, not Bane's.  If you really need to know what char I play, I'd be happy to tell you in private if you wish confirmation that it's truely not Bane, but other than that, My char in game and the char I'm creating of the barmaid will never meet.  Since there is only 1 account allowed on FV, my game char will be handing out the prizes, and my game char will most likely be collecting them as well.  Others in the Fist have told me that they think it's a good idea and some of them may help lessen the strain on my purse strings by giving me donations as well.  This is not a forum OF the fist, but an event sponsored BY the fist.  It's the same as when you go into a bar and see Killian's Red banners hanging around St. Patrick's Day.  Killian's helps sponsor that evening by providing goodies so they get to put up their name and be proud of doing a good thing.<br>
<br>
I have been a gamer on table tops, on networks, solo, and on the internet.  I have a firm grip of game knowledge, out of game knowledge, and that just because one char knows something doesn't mean they all do.  Drixa doesn't care in the least if the Fist is at war with another guild.  If a member of that guild writes the best story for that month, they'll get the prize.  Even if it's about a battle they had with the Fist where the Fist lost.  She doesn't care.  She has a bar to run and any good bartender knows it's in their best interests to keep the peace (or you end up spending all of your profits on new furnature).  <br>
<br>
I posted a few comments to the OOC board and to the FV general discussion board.  I won't repost it here, but please read it and give me your oppinions.  It will be your decision if I open my doors here or not.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubanegrivm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Banegrivm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 203<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/9/01 3:56:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=29.topic&index=33>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A word from the barmaid of Hero Hart Tavern</span><hr size=1> Jusiel, I don't know about that...I've met some rough women in my time.<br>
